scenes.description: Moona and Nerissa leave Raora after completing the limbo challenge.
Raora comments on how Moona and Nerissa are still walking as if they are doing the limbo.
Cinematic shots of the new Sci-Fi themed area.
Raora explores the Sci-Fi area and senses the presence of her next guests.
Fuwawa, Mococo, and Bijou reveal themselves and excitedly greet Raora.
The group performs their official introductions for the 3D debut.
The guests announce the final mini-game: "Run! Run! Raora!!".
Bijou explains the rules while showing the cursed food items Raora must dodge.
